    "insights_summary": "The study investigated the role of epigenetic modulations in spaceflight physiological adaptation in Arabidopsis. The results showed that the elp2-5 plants failed to grow normally in spaceflight, while the met1-7 plants suffered less. The study highlights the importance of epigenetic marking in environmental responses, even during novel environmental stresses outside of the evolutionary history...",
